# IP-Locator

A Python tool to look up IP address location information.

## Features

- Look up any IP address location
- Display country, region, city, ISP, and more
- Command-line interface with ASCII art banner

## Usage

```bash
# Look up a specific IP
python3 ip-locator.py 8.8.8.8

# Get your own IP info
python3 ip-locator.py --my-ip
python3 ip-locator.py -m
```

## Example Output

```
IP Address          : 8.8.8.8
Country             : United States
Region              : Virginia
City                : Ashburn
ISP                 : Google LLC
```

## Requirements

```bash
pip install requests
```

